effects.description:
Yinlin dapat menampung hingga 100 Judgement Points. Yinlin mendapatkan Judgement Points melalui cara-cara berikut:
Saat melancarkan Intro Skill Raging Storm;
Saat Basic Attack Zapstring's Dance mengenai target;
Saat melancarkan Resonance Skill Magnetic Roar;
Saat Resonance Skill Electromagnetic Blast mengenai target;
Saat melancarkan Resonance Skill Lightning Execution.
